# Set the parameters for conjugate model #

N = 1200;   # sample size
n = 1000;  # observations number
q = 2; p = 2; 
 = [3 1
     1 2];
 = [1.0 -1.0
     -5.0 2.0];
1 = 6.0; 1 = 0.5; # parameter for the independent F
 = 0.93;            # 2 / (2 + 2)

# priors #
 = fill(0.0, p, q); V =[[100.0 0.0]; [0.0 100.0]];
 = 2 * q;  = [[1.0 0.0]; [0.0 1.0]];
In [6]:
# Generate simulation data #

Random.seed!(1234);
coords = rand(2, N);                                          # random location over unit square
X = hcat(fill(1, (N,)), rand(N));                             # design matrix
D = pairwise(Euclidean(), coords, dims = 2);                  # distance matrix
1 = exp.(-1 * D);                                           # covariance matrix
F = [rand(MvNormal(1), 1) rand(MvNormal(1), 1)];
U = cholesky().U;
 = F * U; # latent process
Y = X *  +  + transpose(rand(MvNormal( * (1 /  - 1.0)), N));              # response matrix
In [7]:
# Some data preparations #

ordx = sortperm(coords[1, :]);                                # sort order based on the first coordinates
X_ord = X[ordx, :]; Y_ord = Y[ordx, :]; _ord = [ordx, :];   # sorted data
_incp_obs = _ord + fill(1.0, (N, 1)) * transpose([1, :]);  # latent process + intercept
coords_ord = coords[:, ordx];
S = sample(1:N, n, replace = false, ordered = true);          # observed location index for 1st response
M = setdiff(1:N, S);                                          # index of missing data

m = 10;                                                       # number of nearest neighbor                       
NN = BuildNN(coords_ord[:, S], m, 1.0);                       # build nearest neighbor 
nnIndx_col = vcat(NN.nnIndx, 1:n);                            # the index of columns
nnIndx_row = zeros(Int64, 0);                                               
for i in 2:m
    nnIndx_row = vcat(nnIndx_row, fill(i, i-1))
end
nnIndx_row = vcat(nnIndx_row, repeat((m + 1):n, inner = m), 1:n);  # the index of rows

# (a) Randomly split S into K folder 
Random.seed!(34);
kf = 5;
parts = kfoldperm(n,kf);

# (b) Build NN index for training data in ith folder
using RCall
CVNN_train = Array{Any,1}(undef, kf);
CVNN_test = Array{Any,1}(undef, kf);
CVnnIndx_col = Array{Any,1}(undef, kf);
CVnnIndx_row = Array{Any,1}(undef, kf);
CVMnnIndxLU = Array{Any,1}(undef, kf); 
CVMnnIndx = Array{Any,1}(undef, kf);

@rput coords_ord
@rput S
@rput m
@rput parts

for i in 1:kf
    
    # Build NN index for training data in ith folder
    CVNN_train[i] = BuildNN(coords_ord[:, S[filter(x->!(x in parts[i]), eachindex(S))]], m, 1.0);
    CVnnIndx_col[i] = vcat(CVNN_train[i].nnIndx, 1:(n - length(parts[i])));
    CVnnIndx_row[i] = zeros(Int64, 0);
    for j in 2:m
        CVnnIndx_row[i] = vcat(CVnnIndx_row[i], fill(j, j - 1));
    end
    CVnnIndx_row[i] = vcat(CVnnIndx_row[i], 
        repeat((m + 1):(n - length(parts[i])), inner = m), 1:(n - length(parts[i])));
        
    # Build nearest neighbor index for holdout locations
    @rput i
    R"""
    library("RANN")
    nn_mod_ho <- nn2(t(coords_ord[, S[-parts[[i]]]]), t(coords_ord[, S[parts[[i]]]]), k = m)
    """
    @rget nn_mod_ho
    CVNN_test[i] = nn_mod_ho;
    CVMnnIndxLU[i] = collect(1:m:(length(parts[i]) * m + 1));
    CVMnnIndx[i] = vec(nn_mod_ho[:nn_idx]');  
end

In [13]:
# For loop
CVRMSPE = fill(0.0, length(_grid), length(_grid));
prog = Progress(kf, 1, "Computing initial pass...", 50)
for i in 1:kf
    CVnIndx = length(CVNN_train[i].nnIndx);
    nk = length(parts[i]);
    CVA = Array{Float64}(undef, CVnIndx); CVD = Array{Float64}(undef, n - nk);
    Index_train = [filter(x->!(x in parts[i]), eachindex(S))][1];
    CVVK = []; CVXstar = []; CVYstar = []; CVstar = [];
    
    CVAtilde = Array{Float64}(undef, nk * m); CVDtilde = Array{Float64}(undef, nk);
    CVAtildeM = [];
    
    for j in 1:length(_grid) 
        for k in 1:length(_grid)
            
            # obtain posterior estimators of beta
            getAD(coords_ord[:, S[Index_train]], 
                CVNN_train[i].nnIndx, CVNN_train[i].nnDist, CVNN_train[i].nnIndxLU, 
                _grid[j], 0.5, CVA, CVD);
            CVVK = Diagonal(1 ./ sqrt.(CVD)) * (sparse(CVnnIndx_row[i], 
                    CVnnIndx_col[i], vcat(-CVA, ones(n - nk))));
            CVa = sqrt(_grid[k] / (1 - _grid[k]));
            CVXstar = sparse(vcat(repeat(1:(n - nk), 3), repeat((n - nk + 1):(n - nk + p), p)), 
                vcat(repeat(1:p, inner = n - nk), (1 + p):(n - nk + p), repeat(1:p, inner = p)), 
                vcat(vec(CVa * X_ord[S[Index_train], :]), CVa * ones(n - nk), 
                    vec(inv(L.L))), (2 * (n - nk) + p), (p + n - nk));
            CVXstar[(n - nk + p + 1): (2 * (n - nk) + p), (p + 1):(n - nk + p)] = CVVK;
            CVYstar = vcat(CVa * Y_ord[S[Index_train], :], L, fill(0.0, (n - nk, q)));
            CVstar = fill(0.0, n - nk + p, q)
            for l in 1:q
                CVstar[:, l] = lsmr(CVXstar, CVYstar[:, l]);
            end

            # obtain posterior predictions over holded folder
            getAD(coords_ord[:, S[Index_train]], CVMnnIndx[i], 
                vec(CVNN_test[i][:nn_dists]'), CVMnnIndxLU[i],  _grid[j], 0.5, CVAtilde, CVDtilde)
            CVAtildeM = sparse(repeat(1:nk, inner = m), CVMnnIndx[i], CVAtilde, nk, n - nk);
            Y_hold_mean = X_ord[S[parts[i]], :] * CVstar[1:p, 1:q] + 
                CVAtildeM * CVstar[(p + 1):(p + n - nk), 1:q];
            
            # Calculate RMSPE
            CVRMSPE[j, k] = CVRMSPE[j, k] + sqrt(mean((Y_ord[S[parts[i]], :] - Y_hold_mean).^2));
        end
    end
    next!(prog) # monitor the progress
end

# Build * V* * v*

# (a) Lr-1 and Lr-1
L = cholesky(V); 
L = L.L \ ; 

# (b) Construct Xstar Ystar
nIndx = length(NN.nnIndx);
A = Array{Float64}(undef, nIndx); D = Array{Float64}(undef, n);
getAD(coords_ord[:, S], NN.nnIndx, NN.nnDist, NN.nnIndxLU, _pick, 0.5, A, D);
VK = Diagonal(1 ./ sqrt.(D)) * (sparse(nnIndx_row, nnIndx_col, vcat(-A, ones(n))));
a = sqrt(_pick / (1 - _pick));
Xstar = sparse(vcat(repeat(1:n, 3), repeat((n + 1):(n + p), p)), 
        vcat(repeat(1:2, inner = n), (1 + p):(n + p), repeat(1:p, inner = p)), 
        vcat(vec(a * X_ord[S, :]), a * ones(n), vec(inv(L.L))), (2 * n + p), (p + n));
Xstar[(n + p + 1): (2 * n + p), (p + 1):(n + p)] = VK;
Ystar = vcat(a * Y_ord[S, :], L, fill(0.0, (n, q)));

# (c) obtain star star and star
star = fill(0.0, n + p, q)
for i in 1:q
    star[:, i] = lsmr(Xstar, Ystar[:, i]);
end
u = Ystar - Xstar * star;
star =  + u'u; star =  + n;

In [21]:
# generate the posterior samples #
prog = Progress(N_sam, 1, "Computing initial pass...", 50)
for l in 1:N_sam
    
    _sam[:, :, l] = rand(InverseWishart(star, star), 1)[1];    # sample 
    chol_sam = cholesky(_sam[:, :, l]);
    eta = rand(Normal(), 2 * n + p, q) * chol_sam.U;
    for i in 1:q
        v[:, i] = lsmr(Xstar, eta[:, i])
    end
    _sam[:, :, l] = v + star;
    
    z = rand(Normal(), nm, q) * chol_sam.U;
    _M_sam[:, :, l] = AtildeM * _sam[:, :, l] + DtildeD * z
    
    z = rand(Normal(), nm, q) * chol_sam.U;
    Y_M_sam[:, :, l] = X_ord[M, :] * _sam[1:p, 1:q, l] + _M_sam[:, :, l] + 1 / a * z
    next!(prog) # monitor the progress
end
